            <title>[DERBY-2132] EmbeddedDriver should include JDBC 4.0 in the list of versions it supports in its javadoc</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-2132</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Expand this list:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	&amp;lt;UL&amp;gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;LI&amp;gt; JDBC 3.0 - Java 2 - JDK 1.4, J2SE 5.0&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;LI&amp;gt; JDBC 2.0 - Java 2 - JDK 1.2,1.3&lt;br/&gt;
	&amp;lt;/UL&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also may want to add text indicating how the driver is auto loaded with Java SE 6 and beyond&lt;/p&gt;</description>
